content.rendered:
THE JEEP WRANGLER BAR IS AVAILABLE FOR PRE ORDER

We have stock of the new Jeep Wrangler Evolution bar arriving end of April. If you want to guarantee to be one of the first to receive one of these you can pre order one now. Hurry before you miss out! Click here to pre order

-The Evolution Bumper is finished in a hard-wearing Powder coat and available standard in powder coat black or can be optioned colour coded. It is a 3mm steel construction and includes as standard a 5mm Aluminium bash plate not offered on other brands. We also ofer as standard, LED foglights which are an option on many other brands.

-The Evolution bumper has carried out many dynamic crash tests here in Australia to ensure it complements the existing safety systems for example Air bags. The Standard bumper on your vehicle gets removed completely and can be saved / sold.

Includes:

Standard with Winch mount

Integrated LED Foglights

5mm Aluminium Bash / Protection plate

2 x Vehicle recovery points

Optional:

Can be colour coded to your vehicle specification

Bumper fully chromed

Winch

Spotlight bar

Spotlights
